ately favored other options, likely due to the convergence of multiple strong plays in the starting lineup and the presence of a 34% rain risk associated with his matchup against Mitch Keller. We also have **Marcell Ozuna** (62.0) as a starter despite a 34% rain risk due to a strong matchup against Miles Mikolas, where his score is boosted by +19% from the opposing pitcher's xERA.",
